01:50:11.541 --> 01:50:13.131
Well, you are, but...

01:50:15.666 --> 01:50:18.036
What do you
and your dad like to do together?

01:50:18.625 --> 01:50:21.415
When I'm at my dad's,
we sometimes watch a movie

01:50:21.500 --> 01:50:23.000
