02:05:21.541 --> 02:05:23.671
I have the album cover
if anyone needs to reference it.

02:05:23.750 --> 02:05:25.250
And we should leave soon.

02:05:25.333 --> 02:05:27.463
I'm saying that as much for me
as anyone else.

